OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FDonald Trump has invited Chinese
OL,7,FPresident Xi Jinping to visit the
OL,8,FWhite House after a series of talks in
OL,9,FBeijing.
OL,11,FBoth leaders addressed a state banquet
OL,12,Fon Thursday, focusing on the stability
OL,13,Fof relations between the two countries.
OL,15,FTrump invited Xi and his wife, Madame
OL,16,FPeng, to visit the US on September 24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Xi described the
OL,7,Frelationship between the two countries
OL,8,Fas the world's most consequential,
OL,9,Fwarning that both sides must "never
OL,10,Fmess it up".
OL,12,F"Both China and the United States
OL,13,Fstand to gain from cooperation and
OL,14,Flose from confrontation. Our two
OL,15,Fcountries should be partners rather
OL,16,Fthan rivals," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,F"President Trump and I also agreed to
OL,7,Fbuild a constructive China-US
OL,8,Frelationship of strategic stability to
OL,9,Fpromote the steady, sound and
OL,10,Fsustainable development of China-US
OL,11,Frelations and bring more peace,
OL,12,Fprosperity and progress to the world."
OL,14,FTrump said the two countries had "much
OL,15,Fin common," pointing to shared values
OL,16,Fof "hard work," "courage" and
OL,17,F"achievement," adding: "The world is a
OL,18,Fspecial world with the two of us
OL,19,Funited and together."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FAway from the state banquet, trade
OL,7,Fdiscussions have taken precedence over
OL,8,Fthornier issues, including Iran,
OL,9,FTaiwan, Ukraine, and North Korea.
OL,11,FEarlier, in their closed-door meeting,
OL,12,FXi told Trump that if Taiwan is
OL,13,Fhandled well, US-China relations "will
OL,14,Fenjoy overall stability".
OL,16,FIf not, the two countries risk
OL,17,F"clashes and even conflicts, putting
OL,18,Fthe entire relationship in great
OL,19,Fjeopardy," Xi said, according to
OL,20,FChina's official Xinhua News Agency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FBut the Chinese also highlighted how
OL,7,Fpivotal the issue is for Beijing, with
OL,8,Fa foreign ministry spokesperson saying
OL,9,FXi told Trump: "The Taiwan question is
OL,10,Fthe most important issue in China-US
OL,11,Frelations."
OL,13,FThe spokesperson said: "If it is
OL,14,Fhandled properly, the bilateral
OL,15,Frelationship will enjoy overall
OL,16,Fstability. Otherwise, the two
OL,17,Fcountries will have clashes and even
OL,18,Fconflicts, putting the entire
OL,19,Frelationship in great jeopardy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FTrump in December authorised an $11
OL,7,Fbillion (#8.1bn) arms package for
OL,8,FTaiwan, a self-governed island that
OL,9,FBeijing claims as its own territory.
OL,10,FThe US has not yet moved forward with
OL,11,Fdelivery.
OL,13,FTrump heaped praise on Xi, saying:
OL,14,F"You're a great leader. Sometimes
OL,15,Fpeople don't like me saying it, but I
OL,16,Fsay it anyway, because it's true."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FBut Xi was darker in his remarks,
OL,7,Fexpressing hope that the US and China
OL,8,Fcould avoid conflict and asking
OL,9,F"whether the two countries can
OL,10,Ftranscend the 'Thucydides Trap' and
OL,11,Fforge a new model for relations
OL,12,Fbetween major powers".
OL,14,FHe used a term popular in foreign
OL,15,Fpolicy studies, referring to the idea
OL,16,Fthat when a rising power threatens to
OL,17,Fdisplace an established power, the
OL,18,Fresult is often war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,F"Cooperation benefits both sides,
OL,7,Fwhile confrontation harms both," Xi
OL,8,Fsaid. "The two countries should be
OL,9,Fpartners rather than rivals."
OL,11,FXi has mentioned the Thucydides Trap
OL,12,Fbefore about US-China relations,
OL,13,Fdating back as early as 2014.
OL,15,FOn the business and trade front, Xi
OL,16,Fwas more welcoming and said China's
OL,17,Fdoor of opening to US business will
OL,18,Fonly open wider, he told American
OL,19,Fcorporate leaders who accompanied
OL,20,FTrump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778839649
OL,3,CTrump invites Xi Jinping to visit
OL,4,CWhite House after talks in Beijing
OL,6,FThe US president said the business
OL,7,Fleaders all respect and value China,
OL,8,Fand he encourages them to expand
OL,9,Fcooperation with China, Xinhua
OL,10,Freported.
OL,12,FTrump told Xi during another previous
OL,13,Fmeeting with the business leaders that
OL,14,Fincluded the likes of Tesla's Elon
OL,15,FMusk and Apple's Tim Cook, "I didn't
OL,16,Fwant the second or the third in the
OL,17,Fcompany, I wanted only the top, and
OL,18,Fthey're here today to pay respects to
OL,19,Fyou and to China."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
